entries.content: List top prospect objections and frustrations on your website (e.g., in FAQs) to address concerns proactively, build trust, and save sales team time.
entries.notes: Applies objection handling principle to website content, framing value as transparency and efficiency.

entries.content: Prospects often place more trust in organic search listings than paid ads, perceiving earned authority over paid visibility.
entries.notes: Frames organic presence as a unique value point against competitors using paid ads, without direct attack.

focus_area: Competitive Objections: Unique value framing without attacking others
